# MCP Environment — Umbra (example)

> Copiar para `.env` na **raiz do monorepo** (`UMBRA/.env`).  
> **NUNCA** commitar `.env` com valores reais.

# --- SQL Server (user-mssql / sqlserver-plugin) ---
# Database Umbra — dev local via Docker (:1433) ou instância SQL dev
MSSQL_CONNECTION_STRING=

# Alternativa (se o MCP usar vars separadas):
# MSSQL_SERVER=localhost,1433
# MSSQL_DATABASE=Umbra
# MSSQL_USER=
# MSSQL_PASSWORD=

# --- GitHub (github-plugin) ---
# PAT com escopo mínimo; conta umbraotus7 / org Otus7
GITHUB_TOKEN=
GITHUB_OWNER=Otus7

# --- Docker (docker-plugin) ---
# Vazio = Docker Desktop default. Linux: unix:///var/run/docker.sock
DOCKER_HOST=

# --- Azure Entra (azure-plugin — sem MCP; referência appsettings) ---
# AZURE_TENANT_ID=
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# --- Sentry (opcional; plugin disabled no Umbra) ---
# SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=
# SENTRY_ORG=
# SENTRY_PROJECT=
